raaz : reboot is a 2016 indian supernatural thriller film , written and directed by vikram bhatt . the film features emraan hashmi and kriti kharbanda in the lead roles . the film is produced by vishesh bhatt and vishesh bhatt under the banner of vishesh films . the film features emraan hashmi and kajal aggarwal in the lead roles . the film was released worldwide on 6 july 2016 .